metadata.name: Chill Frog #1
metadata.description: Chill Frogs are the chillest collection of 6,000 generative frog NFTs - digital collectibles living on the Ethereum Blockchain. With over 700,000 different combinations no two frogs are the same. All frogs are chill, but some are more chill than others... Who will you mint?  For more info about Chill Frogs and to join our community discord, visit: https://chillfrogs.io/
